{"tid":1879904,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大學生再次不受惠於政府津貼","createTime":"2020-02-14T12:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T17:51:53.000Z","uid":303950,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2b30d9ebafdb9d2c343657c06dea76d536d514d6","tid":1879904,"uid":303950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T12:59:04.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母呀，大學生唔撚係人呀。大得個一兩年當我地無撚敵？綠巨人？勁撚到病毒都殺得死？<br />\n<br />\n中學生都加一千<br />\n我中學個時就派撚曬比大過十八歲<br />\n我大學個時就派撚曬比細過十八歲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一係就減大學學費，一係就派返啲學費，你地班大學高層同淋病傾掂佢！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/2855268284558773/?type=3&amp;source=48&amp;_ft_=qid.6793275497967452581%3Amf_story_key.2606524976226322%3Agroup_id.1400713453474153%3Atop_level_post_id.2606524976226322%3Atl_objid.2606524976226322%3Acontent_owner_id_new.526073317%3Aoriginal_content_id.2855268587892076%3Aoriginal_content_owner_id.710476795704610%3Apage_id.710476795704610%3Asrc.22%3Aphoto_id.2855268284558773%3Astory_location.6%3Aattached_story_attachment_style.photo%3Afilter.GroupStoriesByActivityEntQuery%3Atds_flgs.3%3Apage_insights.%7B&quot;710476795704610&quot;%3A%7B&quot;page_id&quot;%3A710476795704610%2C&quot;actor_id&quot;%3A526073317%2C&quot;attached_story&quot;%3A%7B&quot;page_id&quot;%3A710476795704610%2C&quot;actor_id&quot;%3A710476795704610%2C&quot;dm&quot;%3A%7B&quot;isShare&quot;%3A0%2C&quot;originalPostOwnerID&quot;%3A0%7D%2C&quot;psn&quot;%3A&quot;EntStatusCreationStory&quot;%2C&quot;post_context&quot;%3A%7B&quot;object_fbtype&quot;%3A266%2C&quot;publish_time&quot;%3A1581679180%2C&quot;story_name&quot;%3A&quot;EntStatusCreationStory&quot;%2C&quot;story_fbid&quot;%3A%5B2855268587892076%5D%7D%2C&quot;role&quot;%3A1%2C&quot;sl&quot;%3A6%7D%2C&quot;dm&quot;%3A%7B&quot;isShare&quot;%3A0%2C&quot;originalPostOwnerID&quot;%3A0%7D%2C&quot;psn&quot;%3A&quot;EntGroupMallPostCreationStory&quot;%2C&quot;role&quot;%3A1%2C&q